Message collection filters. Use ! to negate condition. För e Beijschpell bedügg <kbd lang="en" xml:lang="en" dir="ltr">!fuzzy</kbd> dt mer blohß alle di - list non-fuzzy messages. Filters kumme zom drahre en däsällve Reihjefollesch wi se aanjejovve sin.
;<kbd lang="en" xml:lang="en" dir="ltr">fuzzy</kbd>:Messages with fuzzy Makkehrong.
;<kbd lang="en" xml:lang="en" dir="ltr">optional</kbd>:Messages which should be translated blohß wann Änderonge nühdesch sin.
;<kbd lang="en" xml:lang="en" dir="ltr">ignored</kbd>:Messages which are nimmohls övversaz.
;<kbd lang="en" xml:lang="en" dir="ltr">hastranslation</kbd>:Messages which have a translation regardless if it is fuzzy or not.
;<kbd lang="en" xml:lang="en" dir="ltr">translated</kbd>:Messages which have a translation which is not fuzzy.
;<kbd lang="en" xml:lang="en" dir="ltr">changed</kbd>:Messages which has been translated or changed since last export.
;<kbd lang="en" xml:lang="en" dir="ltr">reviewer:</kbd>#:Messages where given user ID # is among reviewers.
;<kbd lang="en" xml:lang="en" dir="ltr">last-translator&#58</kbd>;#:Messages where given user ID # is the last Övversäzer.

apihelp-query+messagegroups-param-prop:
Wat för en Aanjahbe em Zersammehang med Övversäzonge ze holle:
;id:Donn de Kännong vun dä Jropp derbei.
;label:Include label vun dä Jropp.
;description:Include description vun dä Jropp.
;class:Include class name vun dä Jropp.
;namespace:Include Appachtemang vun dä Jropp. Not all groups belong to a single Appachtemang.
;exists:Include self-calculated existence Eijeschaff vun dä Jropp.
;icon:Include URLs to icon vun dä Jropp.
;priority:Include priority status like discouraged.
;prioritylangs:Include preferred Schprohche. If not set, this returns false.
;priorityforce:Include priority status - is the priority Schprohchesetting forced.
;workflowstates:Include the workflow states vun dä Jropp vun Täxte un Nohreeschte.
